    "There were two techniques employed.",
    "Without balancing the data and eliminating outliers, one can use the data straight to machine learning algorithms.",
    "The results obtained were not encouraging.",
    "As a result, we eliminate outliers and balance data before examining the impact of data preparation on classification model performance.",
    "We use state-of-the-art machine learning methods to estimate the sensitivity of a medicine combination based on the vast volume of drug combination data compiled in the O'Neil dataset."
